{% comment %}
  AVA Pay theme app extension — App Embed Block.

  Once a merchant installs the AVA Pay app, this block appears in the
  Shopify theme editor under "App embeds". They click the toggle and AVA Pay
  is live on every page of their storefront — no code changes, no copy/paste.

  The single line below loads our app proxy embed script. The script:
    1. Detects AVA agent fingerprints on storefront page loads.
    2. Calls /apps/ava-pay/verify (HMAC-signed by Shopify on the way to us).
    3. Applies a one-time discount code if the agent is trusted.
{% endcomment %}

<script async src="{{ shop.url }}/apps/ava-pay/embed.js"></script>

{% schema %}
{
  "name": "AVA Pay",
  "target": "head",
  "settings": [
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": "AVA Pay verifies AI shopping agents and applies a one-time discount to verified orders. Configure the discount percentage in the AVA Pay app's Settings page."
    }
  ]
}
{% endschema %}
